window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Ark—humanity’s valiant effort to reach beyond our solar system to establish the first interstellar colony at a distant star. For 300 thousand colonists, the colony brings the promise of a fresh start and for some, a second chance.</p> <p>Connor never meant to escape wrongful imprisonment, nor being put into stasis aboard the Ark. He might be the wrong man for the colony, but he’s the right man to see that it survives what’s coming.</p> <p><i>First Colony</i> is a sprawling science fiction epic. This Omnibus brings you the peak of that adventure where sinister conflict, war, and a mysterious invasion force who has brought about the collapse of entire civilizations, threaten to exterminate the last of humanity.</p> <p>Join Connor Gates and the survivors of Earth as they explore a new world, using every bit of human ingenuity to snatch victory from an unrivaled empire.</p> <p>Science fiction for those who long to explore!</p>"; 
